and they gone on up the line a ways.

55
00:09:38,458 --> 00:09:40,293
Some kind of union bizness.

56
00:09:41,194 --> 00:09:43,562
Yeah, I saw.
- You best steer clear of it.

57
00:09:46,132 --> 00:09:47,900
My name's Bridey Mae Tolliver.

58
00:09:48,801 --> 00:09:51,170
Uh, Joe Kenehan.

59
00:09:51,871 --> 00:09:54,706
Uh, you know

60
00:09:54,707 --> 00:09:57,609
Radnor's Boarding House?
- Big white house.

61
00:09:57,610 --> 00:10:02,013
Right on past the coal dock,
she's a real sourpuss, though...

62
00:10:02,014 --> 00:10:03,049
Elma Radnor.

63
00:10:05,318 --> 00:10:05,951
Thank you.

64
00:10:06,352 --> 00:10:07,720
You gonna be in town long?

65
