73
00:11:21,861 --> 00:11:24,196
Medical doctor provided by the Company
is 2 dollars a month,

74
00:11:24,197 --> 00:11:26,265
special procedures extra.

75
00:11:27,266 --> 00:11:30,206
Your train ride here provided
by the Company will be deducted

76
00:11:30,237 --> 00:11:32,404
from your first month's pay.

77
00:11:32,805 --> 00:11:34,873
Your pay will be issued as Company script,


78
00:11:34,874 --> 00:11:38,844
redeemable for all goods and services
at the Stone Mountain

79
00:11:38,885 --> 00:11:40,679
Company Store.

80
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:43,249
Purchases of any items available
at the Company Store

81
