from jacking up them prices at your store?

84
00:11:52,090 --> 00:11:53,058
Name?

85
00:11:54,359 --> 00:11:57,195
Johnson. They calls me 'Few Clothes'.

86
00:11:59,198 --> 00:12:03,692
Powder, fuses, lamps, head gear
and all appropriate clothing will be

87
00:12:03,703 --> 00:12:05,861
available at the Company Store,

88
